channel.title: Help with PI teleports
channel.description: OK, I know for a fact that everything in clickingbuttons.java is correct but for some odd reason, whenever I set the ardougne teleport (1st and only option) to my custom skiller's area, it won't even send a message or teleport ingame when I click it. I heard the problem can be resolved within actionhandler.java, but where in the huge file can I fix this? Thanks and all help is thanked.
